{"id":20190,"date":"2015-01-20T15:29:35","date_gmt":"2015-01-20T11:29:35","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=20190"},"modified":"2023-02-06T11:59:13","modified_gmt":"2023-02-06T07:59:13","slug":"last-man-to-enter-jannah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/20\/last-man-to-enter-jannah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Paradise: Story of the last man to enter Paradise"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Verily, I know who will be the last to come out of the Hellfire and the last to enter Paradise. He is a man who will come out of the Hellfire crawling. Allah will say to him: Go and enter Paradise. The man will go out but imagine it is full, so he will return and say: O Lord, I have found it full. Allah will say: Go and enter Paradise and you will have as much as the world and ten times more. The man will say: Do You mock me or laugh at me while you are the King?<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6571, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 186<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u0650\u064a \u0644\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0622\u062e\u0650\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0